          <mainBody>
            <p eId="annex_2_p_8"><b>Annex B – Hansard References</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>55 </num>
              <p>The following table sets out the dates and Hansard references for each stage of the Act's passage through Parliament. </p>
            </blockContainer>
            <table uk:widths="1.72in 1.44in 3.14in">
              <tr>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Stage</b></p>
                </th>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Date</b></p>
                </th>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Hansard Reference</b></p>
                </th>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                  <p><i>House of Lords</i></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/bills/lbill/2017-2019/0090/18090.pdf"><u>Introduction</u></a></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>20 March 2018</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/lords/2018-03-20/debates/80C9E423-9818-4E75-A916-0CA87567E916/CivilLiabilityBill(HL)"><u>Vol. 790 Col. 184</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Second Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>24 April 2018</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/lords/2018-04-24/debates/9EE297D1-7EB7-481D-ADAF-70F88B5612F0/CivilLiabilityBill(HL)"><u>Vol. 790 Col. 1479</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Grand Committee</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>10 May 2018</p>
                  <p>15 May 2018</p>
                </td>
